FX Concepts CEO John Taylor Says Global ‘Risk Rally’ Is Coming to an End

-- B y   D a v e   L i e d t k a
-- 
2011-06-06T13:30:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/fx-concepts-ceo-john-taylor-says-global-risk-rally-is-coming-to-an-end.html
John Taylor , founder of the world’s
largest currency-hedge fund, reiterated that the global rally in
higher-yielding assets is coming to an end.   Taylor, chairman of New York-based FX Concepts LLC, said
the firm is betting on declines in the euro and gains in the
yen, in a Bloomberg Television interview.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dave Liedtka at 
 dliedtka@bloomberg.net  